{"tid":1769820,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我都唔知","createTime":"2019-12-05T07:01:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T03:18:43.000Z","uid":319621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d03c055bbcdf703a52d9c97bf08108c0178c5400","tid":1769820,"uid":319621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:01:51.000Z","msg":"對佢有好感 終於鼓起勇氣dm佢 都傾左幾個月到<br />\n佢唔會已讀 又唔會hea覆<br />\n係我無聊 想試吓已讀佢睇下佢會唔會主動搵返我 結果係冇嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前都有機會見到下 但而家連撞佢嘅機會都幾乎冇<br />\n究竟應唔應該試吓約佢 但又好驚俾佢拒絕/嚇親佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係其實日日傾 冇已讀 唔Hea覆 唔代表啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以俾啲意見我<br />\n<br />\n我知呢個時勢唔應該諗呢啲 但真係控制唔到唔諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪屌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />128 1500 維園見 🤚🏻☝🏻"},{"pid":"0513279ba05e432d22381651b4fec5b1eef2510c","tid":1769820,"uid":255980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:02:33.000Z","msg":"男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d342a072643eb150b5e4146d10a5eef567f69f","tid":1769820,"uid":319621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0513279ba05e432d22381651b4fec5b1eef2510c","tid":1769820,"uid":255980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:02:33.000Z","msg":"男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:04:00.000Z","msg":"對方係男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489a02ac994d851deb07eb7c90d488e07b49356c","tid":1769820,"uid":255980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74d342a072643eb150b5e4146d10a5eef567f69f","tid":1769820,"uid":319621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0